-------------------------------Thank you for Downloading my Cooking Pot Feature for Unity----------------------------------
In the feature, You can create item scriptable object that own stat feature withc script.
Developer can change and improve those stats and can add new features
Developer can create recipe scriptable object for a combunation to create specific items with cooking pot.
Items can consume and use to change player stats.
all of those features can change and improve according to development needs.
Follow script commends and examples to improve.
